“Deferred Payment Date” means the date after the
 Restricted Period to which the Participant has elected under the Plan to
 defer receipt of Restricted Shares;

“Designated Affiliate” means the affiliates of the
 Corporation designated by the Committee for purposes of the Plan from time
 to time;

“Eligible Directors” means the Directors and the
 directors of any Designated Affiliate of the Corporation from time to
 time;

“Participant” for the Plan means each Eligible
 Director, Eligible Contractor, and Eligible Employee to whom Restricted
 Share Rights are granted;

“Retirement Date” means the date that a
 Participant ceases to be an Eligible Employee, Eligible Director or
 Eligible Contractor due to the Retirement of the Participant;

“Shares” means the common shares in the capital of
 the Corporation, as adjusted in accordance with the provisions of Article
 Five of this Plan;
